{"tid":1555421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"-適時變通-","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:21:12.000Z","uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae473243cd965e3a7056011a22bbc527446d77e","tid":1555421,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"警察可以扮示威者造反，<br />\n賞鐵封站搞垮民意，<br />\n種種問題都可以懶落示威者到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家政府玩既係民意，<br />\n社會上愈多反對政府聲音既，佢地愈站不住腳。<br />\n要贏首先要贏民意，再贏政府，<br />\n<br />\n因為大量失去良心既警察濫權濫捕，愈黎愈多人關注，<br />\n不過換來嘅就係義士既犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭假撤回，提岀四項行動，<br />\n但另一邊警隊企硬大拘捕，<br />\n點解佢地咁放心亂咁打示威者？<br />\n因為政府跟本就冇放軟過！<br />\n表面上同你握手，但實際上隻手鑲滿晒釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推算黎緊政府會更強硬！<br />\n甚至玩更多陰招！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極需保持頭腦清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住Be water，除左流水式運作，水能載舟亦能覆舟。</span><br />\n<br />\n支撐住呢場運動既係各位！千萬不要放棄！<br />\n依家需要既係諗變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">贏翻個公道！同埋五大訴求！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cdf6b50c5b7c8f046e7730f8a7732f312c0753f9","tid":1555421,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283c888995e5ec223cb99a45312f1eb1ce0689e0","tid":1555421,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1483ae74fe3e46170815e245e434314449b468","tid":1555421,"uid":177851,"like":0,"d